	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well when I was level 16 with my third mage I got my focus items fairly easily.<br><br>Got to Cazic Thule and ask the person who is camping the avatar of fear for the broom, stein, torch, and shovel.<br><br>Make an enchanter character with a lot of charisma and go buy all of the gems needed from a gem shop.<br><br>For the giant toes just do some /who alls and look for higher level players that are in Rathe Mountains, Everfrost, and Solusek B. They will sell or give you the giant toes you need.<br><br>You can get the other 4 components very easily by yourself. A fire drake scale, a mermaid scale, a gargoyle eye, and a griffon feather. Check Galuvyen's Focus Item Post. He did a good job of listing the items you need.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
