	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Magician pets are much better. Magician's have a much wider selection of pets to use in different situations, and magicians get focus items which make their pets even stronger. All the magician pets excpet the fire pet can tank better than the necro skelaton pet. ALL of the magician pets will outdamage the skelaton pet. <br><br>Of course its not all about pets. Necro's have DoT's that are much more efficient than magician DD's (once a necro gets to level 12 anyway) and necro's have TONS of ways to get out of sticky situations where as magicians have....gate.<br><br>If you are just starting the game I would suggest a High Elf Magician. You probably don't want the bad faction that comes along with being a necro.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
	   </form></table><ul>

